beer.beer_description:
I don't want a lot for Christmas, there is just one beer I need...

This Christmas, unwrap the gift of flavour with our tasty Amber Ale. With a rich copper hue and caramel sweetness it's perfectly balanced with floral and citrus notes from classic American hops. A smooth festive brew that'll jingle your taste buds all the way!
